title: Australia’s Home-Price Gains Accelerate Even as Rate Hike Looms
description: Australia’s home-price growth gathered pace in January, underscoring the challenge for Reserve Bank policymakers as they weigh interest-rate increases in a property market already grappling with stretched affordability.
